comments.body:
Hi i do agree, on it being ssp  borealis rather then the one i know which is  ssp europea. Just because it say Ontario has the ssp borealis, and the Yukon has the ssp europea. 
I still call i Trientalis, but when you say  it has changed , i trust that that is so.
